==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rightness
<hw>Right"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS. <ets>rihtnes</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Straightness; <as>as, the <ex>rightness</ex> of a line</as>.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The quality or state of being right; right
relation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The craving for <qex>rightness</qex> with God.</q> <rj><qau>J. C.
Shairp.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Right-running</ent>⟦br⟧
